DefaultMessage.SourceString: The IO is in <enemy>shambles</> and crawling with <enemy>moles,</> so if Slone offers you a job, <b>don't be too flattered. </>
But if I were involved, I'm sure I'd be a <b>highly decorated</> field agent.
As for me, I've got <b>nothing to prove. </>

<enemy>To 100%. </>
But if <b>you</> join, you could change that for at least a <b>little while. </>
You're picking up what I'm putting down here, <b>right?</>

I'll give <b>Doctor Slone</> this, 
she's consistent.
I wouldn't say I support the IO...
But I always make sure <b>they support me. </>
I should warn you that the <enemy>mortality rate</> for junior agents has gone <b>up...</>
I am <b>not cleared</> to discuss my involvement or non-involvement with the IO.
